  FORM sub_pre_points_tab .


    LOOP AT t_review_it_act ASSIGNING FIELD-SYMBOL(<l_review_it>).

      APPEND INITIAL LINE TO t_points_tab ASSIGNING FIELD-SYMBOL(<l_points_tab>).

      <l_points_tab>-defect_cat     = <l_review_it>-defect_cat     .
      <l_points_tab>-issue_no       = <l_review_it>-point_counter  .
      <l_points_tab>-obj_name       = <l_review_it>-obj_name       .
      <l_points_tab>-obj_type       = <l_review_it>-obj_type       .
